  <thing id="spSGCrpHz4" name="Corrupt Haze" description="This spell creates a murky aura of profane energy around you. Any good creature striking you with a melee weapon (except reach  weapons), natural weapon, or unarmed strike takes 1d6 points of unholy damage +1 point per two caster levels (maximum +10), and becomes sickened for 1 round (Will negates). If a creature is already sickened, add one round to the duration of the condition.\n\nThe aura also diminishes the impact of holy attacks. You only take half damage from effects that preferentially harm evil creatures, such as holy smite or the extra damage caused by holy weapons. If such an attack allows a Will save for half damage, you take no damage on a successful saving throw. This spell has no impact on additional afflictions caused by these effects, such as the blindness caused by holy smite." compset="Spell">
