  <thing id="spSGInctGr" name="Incite Greed" description="The target is compelled to steal a specific, visible item of your choice. The theft may be carried out in any reasonable manner, but the target may not take any actions, other than in self-defense, that do not help with this goal. The target receives a +2 morale bonus on any combat maneuver or skill check involved in the theft. This spell does not compel the target to take any obviously life-threatening actions. This spell’s effect ends immediately if the target is attacked by anyone (including the item’s possessor).\n\nOnce the item is in the target’s possession, the target cannot take any action that he reasonably believes will lead to losing the item." compset="Spell">
